fe keeping,\nConsult us confidentially about this important\nmutter. Valuable papers kept for you free.\nJ. C. Paul, Ties. Kay. Whealley. Cashiee.\nAvery Turner, V. Tres, Chas. A. Fiik.Jr. Sec'y.\nHOCKADAV PAINTS\nOILS and COAL TAR\nFENC12 POSTS, Etc\nKILL the COUGH\nAND CURE the LUNGS\nDr. King's\nWITH\nNow Discovery\nPRICH\nniur uuuna toe not.\nI wii VOLDS Trial BoHlaOaa\nAND ALL THROAT AND LUNO TROUBLES.\nGUARANTEED 8ATI8BACX0BT\nOB MONEY REFUNDED.\n1","height":"28288","width":"21116"}}
